cp|8|AT|

^B@2^*BLarry Cohen: ^*N|cp||at|I would like to add a few word to the discussion. As the late, great Edgar Kaplan used to say: “Takeout doubles are meant to be taken out.” However, takeout doubles, as is the case for all doubles, can be “converted” for penalty. A very good (at least five cards) suit is needed to leave-in a 1-level takeout double. Let me show you my first example.|
