^*BLarry Cohen: ^*N|cp||at|A leave-in double is okay with this hand.|mb|p|
PG| ***** 109 ***** |


nt||cp|8|AT|^B@2
^*BLarry Cohen: ^*N|cp||at|The higher the level, the less stringent the requirements. On the three-level, a double is often left in with only a decent four-card suit. Especially if it was a balancing double, and you are behind the bidder, a leave-in is possible as the lessor of evils.|
PG| ***** 110 ***** |


NT||bt||
