^B@2^*BHoward: ^*N|cp||at|4S-4N is takeout for any 2 suits (not just clubs and diamonds). So the partner of the 4N bidder must take into account partner could have hearts and diamonds or hearts and clubs. So if it goes, 4S-4N-P-5C-P-5D, then the 4N bidder has hearts and diamonds.|
