NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*BHoward: ^*N|cp||at|Let me add a few points on the limits for the takeout double. I would guess it is equally split between 3S and 4H being the upper limit for takeout doubles. Many experts play doubles of 4-level bids are "card showing", not purely takeout, and partner can and should leave them in unless they have a long suit.|
